01:23:24.000 --> 01:23:26.000
Here we use

01:23:26.000 --> 01:23:28.000
the definition of body Q,

01:23:28.000 --> 01:23:30.000
which is to use its group delay

01:23:30.000 --> 01:23:32.000
and its S11

01:23:32.000 --> 01:23:34.000
to calculate its Q value.

01:23:34.000 --> 01:23:36.000
Its definition of Q is

01:23:36.000 --> 01:23:38.000
similar to the traditional one,

01:23:38.000 --> 01:23:40.000
but through a new formula,

01:23:40.000 --> 01:23:42.000
which is the formula of body Q,

01:23:42.000 --> 01:23:44.000
it can equalize

01:23:44.000 --> 01:23:46.000
every Q value

01:23:46.000 --> 01:23:48.000
on this resonance scale,

01:23:48.000 --> 01:23:50.000
and it can be seen that

01:23:50.000 --> 01:23:52.000
the highest Q value

01:23:52.000 --> 01:23:54.000
of the resonator

01:23:54.000 --> 01:23:56.000
we designed

01:23:56.000 --> 01:23:58.000
is about 960,

01:23:58.000 --> 01:24:00.000
and the carbon

01:24:00.000 --> 01:24:02.000
is about 25.5%.

01:24:02.000 --> 01:24:04.000
Therefore,

01:24:04.000 --> 01:24:06.000
FOM is about 245.

01:24:06.000 --> 01:24:08.000
Compared with the traditional

01:24:08.000 --> 01:24:10.000
F-bar resonator,

01:24:10.000 --> 01:24:12.000
its performance indicator

01:24:12.000 --> 01:24:14.000
is between 100 and 200.

01:24:14.000 --> 01:24:16.000
Therefore,

01:24:16.000 --> 01:24:18.000
more than 200

01:24:18.000 --> 01:24:20.000
indicates that

01:24:20.000 --> 01:24:22.000
the component we designed

01:24:22.000 --> 01:24:24.000
has a certain performance.

01:24:24.000 --> 01:24:26.000
At least,

01:24:26.000 --> 01:24:28.000
it may outperform

01:24:28.000 --> 01:24:30.000
some low-performance

01:24:30.000 --> 01:24:32.000
F-bar components.

01:24:32.000 --> 01:24:34.000
We also

01:24:34.000 --> 01:24:36.000
measured

01:24:36.000 --> 01:24:38.000
the power handling

01:24:38.000 --> 01:24:40.000
of this resonator.

01:24:40.000 --> 01:24:42.000
It can be seen

01:24:42.000 --> 01:24:44.000
that

01:24:44.000 --> 01:24:46.000
compared with

01:24:46.000 --> 01:24:48.000
the previously released

01:24:48.000 --> 01:24:50.000
SYNFIN

01:24:50.000 --> 01:24:52.000
lithium-ion battery components,

01:24:52.000 --> 01:24:54.000
this SO-TYPE

01:24:54.000 --> 01:24:56.000
resonator

01:24:56.000 --> 01:24:58.000
does not have

01:24:58.000 --> 01:25:00.000
any significant

01:25:00.000 --> 01:25:02.000
fluctuation

01:25:02.000 --> 01:25:04.000
after 10 dBm RF power.

01:25:04.000 --> 01:25:06.000
Therefore,

01:25:06.000 --> 01:25:08.000
