01:36:02.000 --> 01:36:04.000
For example,

01:36:04.000 --> 01:36:06.000
when you simulate

01:36:06.000 --> 01:36:08.000
the design of

01:36:08.000 --> 01:36:10.000
multi-modem

01:36:10.000 --> 01:36:12.000
